titles.title: Electing Members to serve on the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on House Administration.
Mr. Ney asked unanimous consent to discharge from committee and consider.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 3/25/2003--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced in the House on March 11, 2003. The summary of that version is repeated here.)Elects specified Members to the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.
